Package: sbivar
Type: Package
Title: Test for Spatial Bivariate Association Across Omics Types
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Stijn", family = "Hawinkel", 
    email = "stijn.hawinkel@psb.ugent.be", 
    role=c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4501-5180")))
Description: The sbivar package implements a suite of tests for bivariate spatial
    association across omics modalities with disjoint coordinate sets. Implemented
    tests are generalized additive models, modified t-test, bivariate Moran's I 
    and Gaussian processes. Both single images and replicated experiments can be
    analysed.
License: GPL-2
